high_descs: Turn left, go forward, after passing the shelves turn right, go right and forward to the part of the desk where the bowl is, left of the computer.
Take the watch in front of the keys from the desk.
Stay at the desk.
Put the keys in the bowl.
Take the bowl from the desk.
Go to the right and face the clock on the desk.
Put the bowl on the shelf below the computer on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a watch in it on a shelf in a desk.

high_descs: Turn left, move forward toward the door, then turn right and go around the wall, then turn left to approach the desk.
Pick up the watch on the desk.
Look up to view the bowl on the desk.
Put the watch into the bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the watch in it from the desk.
Turn around and move forward, then turn left, step forward, then turn left and look down to face the shelf beneath the desk.
Put the bowl on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a watch in it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and walk around to the other side of the wall, veering right to the right side of the desk.
Pick up the watch near the keys on the desk.
Look to the left of the laptop.
Place the watch in the gray bowl.
Pick up the bowl.
Take a step right.
Place the bowl on the shelf under the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a watch in it on a shelf.
